  m_Name: QuestionChoice5
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::QuestionChoiceData
  Question: As the rhythm fades, the Wolf moves to pat your head. "You played so
    well, Ruby. Come here and give me a big hug to show we are friends now."
  option1: "I\u2019m glad you liked the music, but I\u2019m not comfortable with
    hugs. A high-five or a wave is better for me."
  option2: Since I am the Celestial Weaver, I have to be nice to everyone, so okay.
  option3: "I\u2019ll give you a hug, but only if the Starry Merchant isn't looking."
